|3 |    └─SUBPLAN FILTER         |    |1       |18          |
|4 |      ├─TABLE RANGE SCAN     |T   |1       |3           |
|5 |      └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET|C   |1       |16          |
=============================================================
